  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Looking Glass - Looking Glass</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="LookingGlass - Open source PHP looking glass">
    <meta name="author" content="Telephone">

    <!-- IE6-8 support of HTML elements -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->

    <!-- Styles -->
    <link href="assets/css/cerulean.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="assets/css/custom.css" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Container -->
    <div class="container">

      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="header nohighlight" id="overview">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="span12">
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Network Information -->
      <section id="information">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="span12">
            <div class="well">
              <span id="legend">Joe's DC Network Looking Glass</span><!-- IE/Safari dislike <legend> out of context -->
              <p>Server Location: <b>Joes Datacenter, 1325 Tracy Ave, Kansas City, MO 64106</b></p>
              <div style="margin-left: 10px;">
                <p>Test IPv4: 208.94.245.2</p>
                <p></p>
                <p>Test files: <a href="100MB.test" id="testfile">100MB</a> <a href="1000MB.test" id="testfile">1000MB</a> <a href="5000MB.test" id="testfile">5000MB</a> </p>
              </div>
              <p>Your IP Address: <b><a href="#tests" id="userip">164.70.99.9</a></b></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Network Tests -->
      <section id="tests">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="span12">
            <form class="well form-inline" id="networktest" action="#results" method="post">
              <fieldset>
                <span id="legend">Network Tests</span>
                <div id="hosterror" class="control-group">
                  <div class="controls">
                    <input id="host" name="host" type="text" class="input-large" value="164.70.99.9" placeholder="Host or IP address">
                  </div>
                </div>
                <select name="cmd" class="input-medium" style="margin-left: 5px;">
                  <option value="ping" selected="selected">ping</option>
                  <option value="host">host</option>
                  <option value="mtr">mtr</option>
                  <option value="traceroute">traceroute</option>
				                                                                        </select>
                <button type="submit" id="submit" name="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-left: 10px;">Run Test</button>
              </fieldset>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Results -->
      <section id="results" style="display:none">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="span12">
            <div class="well">
              <span id="legend">Results</span>
              <pre id="response" style="display:none"></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
	  
      <!-- Network Graphs -->
      <section id="information">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="span12">
            <div class="well">
              <span id="legend">Backbone Network Utilization</span><!-- IE/Safari dislike <legend> out of context -->
              <div class="weathermap">
                <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Network Weathermap">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
 
    </div><!-- /container -->

    <!-- Javascript -->
    <script src="assets/js/jquery-1.11.2.min.js"></script>
    <script src="assets/js/LookingGlass.min.js"></script>
    <script src="assets/js/XMLHttpRequest.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
